Note : * stratify only works with categorical / discrete labels — not continuous ones. *
| Situation                        | Use `stratify`? |
| -------------------------------- | --------------- |
| Classification (discrete labels) | ✅ Yes           |
| Regression (continuous labels)   | ❌ No            |



